 von grundlegender Bedeutung.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aCatechisms, German. 0aSocinianism. 4aAntitrinitarismus. 4aRakower Katechimus. 4aSoner-Katechismus. 4aSozinianismus. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aSchmeisser, Martin, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Geschichte 2005-2012z9783110346787oZDB-23-OGS0 cprintz978305005200740uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978305005851140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050058511423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783050058511/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OGSc2005d2012